{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20943, "create_time": 1641267355, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "啥考试？", "timestamp": 1641267355}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20946, "create_time": 1641267979, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "啊这，心理原因缓考，之前看到树洞有人分享缓考经验：有睡过的假装有心理原因立即办了缓考，我也不确定", "timestamp": 1641267979}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20949, "create_time": 1641268604, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "赶紧办缓考可能还有救", "timestamp": 1641268604}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20950, "create_time": 1641268623, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "不然铁定吃F", "timestamp": 1641268623}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20951, "create_time": 1641268646, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "装抑郁症", "timestamp": 1641268646}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20953, "create_time": 1641268685, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "，，，", "timestamp": 1641268685}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20958, "create_time": 1641269497, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Eve: 补办缓考需要任课老师证明没有参加考试，然后审批也要严格一点，必须让老师相信确实是突发原因不能考试，或者是缓考手续来不及办完。考后突然开个抑郁症证明可能很难说服老师，建议伪装突发急病", "timestamp": 1641269497}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20959, "create_time": 1641269959, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Eve: 只能缓考死马当活马医了，说实话不一定能办成，但不办肯定会挂科。考试人数开考后学校教务都会统计的，缺考的会被标记，所以任课老师是不可能单独给你组织补考。现在是疫情期间，也许装发烧、腹泻等症状会是一条有效的途径，以上意见仅供参考，如果你有别的急病可以装也可以。", "timestamp": 1641269959}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20972, "create_time": 1641272533, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Eve: 之前有人说过#6785，但我个人觉得补办缓考最好不要用抑郁或者心悸之类的借口。赶紧去校医院装病、开证明，教学门户下载缓考申请表，然后补办缓考。今天中午和下午赶紧去行动，晚了就真的来不及了。最好先打电话问问注册中心补办需要什么具体流程", "timestamp": 1641272533}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 21031, "create_time": 1641288699, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 6, "text": "[tmp]\n怎么非赶上今天发。。。我是今天真的碰到紧急情况准备去缓考的，要是教务看到洞主这洞以为我骗人就跳进黄河洗不清了", "timestamp": 1641288699}], "create_time": 1641267214, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1641288699, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 7306, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "期末考缺考了有补救方式吗？孩子把早上的考试给忘了啊啊啊", "timestamp": 1641267214}}